Name: Starlight  Emerald Lv.2
Description: Through Gemcrafting, raw ore can be processed into a higher-level Emerald.
Description$english: Through Gemcrafting, raw ore can be processed into a higher-level Emerald.
Description2$english: A precious raw stone grown in Regnus, displaying a green hue like a deep lake in the basin. A breeze sweeps through the valley, leaves dance lightly, standing like feathers on the green waves.
